Preliminary to make life easy:
sudo apt-get install sfml-dev

to:
	compile to obj files                              make a library									link the files																																															put exec	    clear the obj files
	g++ -c -std=c++17 -I ./include/ ./src/*.cpp && ar rcs BGraphics.a BGraphic.o && g++ *.a *.o -lsfml-graphics -lsfml-window -lsfml-audio -lsfml-system -lsfml-network -g -pthread -o ./binFile/linuxBuild && rm *.o

to run the Game:
	From ./TankGame
	./binFile/linuxBuild
